| [[Kitty Kallen]]
| 11 September 1954  
| "[[Little Things Mean a Lot]]"
| Despite scoring other hits in her native United States, Kallen never achieved another hit on the UK Chart, which at this point was a mere Top 12.<ref name=occkallen>{{cite web|title=Kitty Kallen - Full Official Chart History|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/artist/1218/kitty-kallen/|website=Official Charts Company|publisher=Official Charts Company|accessdate=19 January 2016}}</ref>
