| [[The Dream Weavers]]
| March/April 1956
| "[[It's Almost Tomorrow]]"
| In the US, they scored a minor hit some months later, but then faded into obscurity there also.<ref name=occdream>{{cite web|title=Dreamweavers - Full Official Chart History|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/artist/3128/dreamweavers/|website=Official Charts Company|publisher=Official Charts Company|accessdate=19 January 2016}}</ref><ref>[http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/bio/index.jsp?pid=158616 Billboard - Artist biography]</ref>
